<div id="manual-tab" class="tab-content">
  <div class="manual-setup">
    <h2><i data-lucide="file-text" style="width:22px;height:22px;"></i> Manual Token Setup</h2>
    <p><strong>Perfect for collaborators or when OAuth isn't working!</strong></p>
    
    <h3 style="margin-top:20px;">Step 1: Create Custom App in Shopify</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Go to: <code>https://your-store.myshopify.com/admin</code></li>
      <li>Click: <strong>Settings</strong> (bottom left)</li>
      <li>Click: <strong>Apps and sales channels</strong></li>
      <li>Click: <strong>"Develop apps"</strong> (top right)</li>
      <li>Click: <strong>"Create an app"</strong></li>
      <li>Name it: <code>My Manager App</code></li>
      <li>Click: <strong>"Configure Admin API scopes"</strong></li>
      <li>Select these checkboxes:
        <ul style="margin-left:20px; margin-top:5px;">
          <li><i data-lucide="check-square" style="width:14px;height:14px;color:var(--accent-primary);"></i> <code>read_products</code></li>
          <li><i data-lucide="check-square" style="width:14px;height:14px;color:var(--accent-primary);"></i> <code>write_products</code></li>
          <li><i data-lucide="check-square" style="width:14px;height:14px;color:var(--accent-primary);"></i> <code>read_orders</code></li>
          <li><i data-lucide="check-square" style="width:14px;height:14px;color:var(--accent-primary);"></i> <code>write_orders</code></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Click: <strong>"Save"</strong></li>
      <li>Click: <strong>"Install app"</strong></li>
      <li>Copy the <strong>"Admin API access token"</strong> (starts with <code>shpat_</code>)</li>
    </ol>
    
    <h3 style="margin-top:20px;">Step 2: Add Token to This App</h3>
    <form onsubmit="addManualToken(event)">
      <input 
        type="text" 
        id="manualShop" 
        placeholder="your-store.myshopify.com" 
        required
      />
      <input 
        type="text" 
        id="manualToken" 
        placeholder="shpat_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx" 
        required
      />
      <button type="submit"><i data-lucide="save" style="width:16px;height:16px;"></i> Add Store Manually</button>
    </form>
    
    <div id="manualResult"></div>
  </div>
</div>
